  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c266e941-1741-4dc6-b659-35fe330cad8f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ECE2B828-5332-4F69-BF1B-53A2D228EC1B\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-C65DFDCD-B9FB-4751-9DE9-9B04E05CC662\">요즘 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-C6AB3DDC-DA79-43E2-94DF-406F53022E21\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-04BF2D61-A517-4247-A123-93D5BD29D7A6\">chat GPT 가   &quot;SO HOT&quot; 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5A530948-E9B6-4B4F-8335-126AEDCA3F70\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-A48C6050-5C72-410B-A4CC-6CC049980935\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-83BF661F-58E1-4688-80F2-334170993E18\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-FFDA7457-BFCD-47D2-8A94-71D54BC9EB61\">AI의 시대가 성큼 다가온 느낌입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5CF855B6-CFC4-463B-BB3E-074788F7FB86\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-EAB3422A-A726-4804-8B60-B98771D1FD95\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9A6C7C40-AA69-40AB-8BD8-31AF427C0095\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-D60708D4-EFA5-4ED9-9530-E94902C88605\">많은 유저들이 독창적인 질문에 어떤 답변을 할지 궁금해서 이런저런 질문놀이를 많이 하고 있더군요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-86ED65BD-A09F-4FDC-8B34-2A116E74CF6F\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-444E9067-27F1-4278-9EDB-7F987046AFD2\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8320AA69-A1C9-41B8-8580-D718D5620A2F\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-E01003CA-15D4-4445-935F-95C1B3579CF1\">그래서,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-60A7870A-9DB2-4F74-8DBA-9A9E3E770790\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-91F26FBF-B952-4321-B35E-ECCF0DF4ECA5\">chatGPT에게 &quot;한의학의 장점&quot;을 물었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-EB7B1D34-D0A0-45AA-BF2A-51DC5150C002\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8A6A0635-9898-41A5-8E81-0A72734B952E\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9A663D0A-80E7-4CCD-9B28-26B8370136CE\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4F703713-8AC9-424C-A930-0567FA57DA83\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-29d79dc1-0711-40ac-922a-b05ef448b9f4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" 