로 &#x27;전인 치료&#x27;라고 하기도 합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-A2E934FC-179F-4B1D-AADE-D0AF9E8BDBC7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-F424298F-3706-4783-90A5-BF399D3BAF97\">부분 부분의 &#x27;병&#x27;에 집중하기보다 몸 전체의 생리, 병리적 상황을 더 중시하는 거죠.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-B7D87DAF-7498-42EF-B1B6-B7FCF7ABB7AA\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-F7FEEAB7-D464-4C7C-A738-8676E958E30F\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-A729DBC2-8E0E-49B0-B68F-953809CCB368\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4D392D31-407E-4428-BDFB-AEDC897CDD08\">특정한 병이 생길 수 있는 &#x27;몸 상태&#x27;를 진단한다고 보시면 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2EA96B46-C0DB-481E-AB37-9C6756A8A6C0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-D365D05A-7E47-4B6B-983B-A4CE39A5C12B\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ACC976E9-A802-465D-BBF4-D3BAA0340AD5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2D258F3A-3C5F-45C0-BF63-9459C18DD35D\">감기 걸렸을 때, 콧물 기침 가래 등 &#x27;증상&#x27;도 치료해야 하지만 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5197D3B2-2BD0-42DB-ADDF-9C03699B4C4B\">감기가 걸릴만한 몸 상태도 파악을 해서 함께 해결해 주면 더 좋은 거죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-CDCC788B-D2D3-4816-8896-1A029294C66B\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6D78EF0D-D602-421A-AA29-5ACF5C87EA3B\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-71E713F6-01E2-4C21-9882-1C5A5C9F204B\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7891AF77-F9B9-4EE8-8D50-8B727A533EB7\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-29865c3c-dc07-4258-afe7-9e0c688c4bde\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-29865c3c-dc07-4258-afe7-9e0c688c4bde\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMTI3/MDAxNjgxNzI1NDgxMDI1.5_8sIQ_v-nq5JgwLgJNpKu-ehaQSupy9rmMT3c77zKkg.8DpDzP3GXkUaknRkEKdqY2ia-uIptoaGXtiviyxya6kg.JPEG.isuhani/2_%EB%B3%B5%EC%82%AC.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMTI3/MDAxNjgxNzI1NDgxMDI1.5_8sIQ_v-nq5JgwLgJNpKu-ehaQSupy9rmMT3c77zKkg.8DpDzP3GXkUaknRkEKdqY2ia-uIptoaGXtiviyxya6kg.JPEG.isuhani/2_%EB%B3%B5%EC%82%AC.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMTI3/MDAxNjgxNzI1NDgxMDI1.5_8sIQ_v-nq5JgwLgJNpKu-ehaQSupy9rmMT3c77zKkg.8DpDzP3GXkUaknRkEKdqY2ia-uIptoaGXtiviyxya6kg.JPEG.isuhani/2_%EB%B3%B5%EC%82%AC.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3c00b645-de50-4675-9584-47aac28d5c0e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-B2E2D133-45C3-4C17-8E9E-34F885952FA9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0099C84D-AB71-4D3B-95B9-BF388FF4D1B8\">특히나 한약처방의 경우 개인 맞춤형 치료죠. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-604EB1B5-4099-4989-9209-DBDC8428F26E\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-60F9B550-E48B-439B-B5F6-D22087134110\">같은 병이라도, 개개인의 특성 (추위를 탄다, 더위를 탄다 / 변비 경향이다 설사 경향이다 등)을 고려해서 처방을 하거든요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-09026B6D-8596-4A25-B637-752CC0A93998\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-D018B42D-CB88-48C9-898C-3A5B1FEDA41E\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0c263bc8-8418-4dd0-b5f7-2e6a7c37dad9\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0c263bc8-8418-4dd0-b5f7-2e6a7c37dad9\", \"src\" : \"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMTYz/MDAxNjgxNzI1NDg2Njk5.spXU318DW3u8gOlVk3u_KnEuByuJ9YpTdAdg-925EhUg.nCchrvB82D6u0Q41Card0r7bostJMrXwbO2MV0cSJvEg.JPEG.isuhani/3_%EB%B3%B5%EC%82%AC.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMTYz/MDAxNjgxNzI1NDg2Njk5.spXU318DW3u8gOlVk3u_KnEuByuJ9YpTdAdg-925EhUg.nCchrvB82D6u0Q41Card0r7bostJMrXwbO2MV0cSJvEg.JPEG.isuhani/3_%EB%B3%B5%EC%82%AC.jpg?type=w80_blur\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAyMzA0MTdfMTYz/MDAxNjgxNzI1NDg2Njk5.spXU318DW3u8gOlVk3u_KnEuByuJ9YpTdAdg-925EhUg.nCchrvB82D6u0Q41Card0r7bostJMrXwbO2MV0cSJvEg.JPEG.isuhani/3_%EB%B3%B5%EC%82%AC.jpg?type=w580\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9f6f75e0-1da4-4d3f-8d79-3fd01999012b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2F330FBF-C83F-4047-ADAE-CFCDF4AC567E\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-74A21CB5-CF99-4276-BB03-C9744A89DA4F\">한약의 재료인 한약재는 공장에서 화학공정을 거쳐 생산하지 않고, 자연에서 재배하거나 재취한 거잖아요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-E24CDE80-7E2A-457C-B8BB-C87FB9F5394F\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3A3159B3-63FB-484B-9304-1369BBA42714\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-E2AFAE8B-7362-4D8B-BD9C-E641F9F3A2B9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-A5814713-76D1-4527-825F-79E8E8C3B110\">쌀도 한약 재고 도라지도 한약재죠. 우리가 일상적으로 먹는 먹거리도 환자를 종합적이고 개별적인 진단한 결과 도라지가 처방되야겠다고 판단이 되면 한약처방을 구성할 때 도라지도 처방하는 겁니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-D976DA07-DBC4-4A5E-BF67-112F01CA6354\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-33241871-DF9B-449A-9DAC-90E07DB87097\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-613CEDFA-47BD-466E-BCDF-FCB882131ADC\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-92C2B7B5-BBE0-46A3-9C73-143129BB52CB\">그래서 밥이 보약이 될 수도 있고, 좋은 식사가 몸을 건강하게 해줄 수도 있겠죠?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5F956458-78CF-4655-9123-063CF6762254\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-FC136E93-E10D-44FB-9DCD-B463155D47E1\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-703A114F-6464-4374-AF96-00052EDB81A9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-B221994C-F400-4CEE-85E9-CF1A85838C65\">병을 치료하거나 기력을 회복시켜야 할 때는 한약을 복용하면 되고요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-97074E33-1243-4EB9-9279-B413A7BFD5E9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-048F0D6F-2933-4E12-AF89-E5D1BC8D159F\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e3f53761-8359-4041-86f4-c229d524d0f6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                           